| Hebrew (Gen 2:7) | Yes — *wayyippaḥ nishmat ḥayyim* | dust from ground | living *nefesh* → "speaking spirit" (Onkelos) | (b)/(c) — emanation (Ramban) |
| Quranic (15:29; 38:72) | Yes — *nafakhtu fīhi min rūḥī* | *ṣalṣāl min ḥamaʾ masnūn* / *ṭīn* | life + *al-asmāʾ kullahā* | (b) honorific + (c) installed |
| Inca (Betanzos) | **NULL** — stone + paint + voice | stone slabs | identity assignment | (c) by naming |
| Inca (Huarochirí) | **NULL** | n/a | n/a | NULL |
